  <h1>Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia</h1>
  <p>Discover one of South East Asia's hidden gems. A melting pot of cultures comes together to create a new, unique hybrid culture. You'll experience unique food, tradition, cultural practices, local customs specifically unique to this area.</p>

  <h2>
    Packages
  </h2>

  <p>You have the option to choose Group Travels, or private tours with us. The summary of the packages can be seen below.</p>

<ul><a href="https://www.freecodecamp.org/learn" target="_blank">Group Travels</a>
  <li>Duration: 7 days</li>
  <li>Places: Petronas Towers, Batu Caves, KL Tower, Merdeka Square, Jalan Alor (food), Aquaria KLCC, Royal Selangor Visitor Centre.</li>
  <li>Transporation: Tour bus</li>
  <li>Languages: English</li>
  <li>Cost: RM 1,000 per person</li>
</ul>


<ul><a href="https://www.freecodecamp.org/learn" target="_blank">Private Tours</a>
  <li>Duration: 7 days</li>
  <li>Places: Petronas Towers, Batu Caves, KL Tower, Merdeka Square, Jalan Alor (food), Aquaria KLCC, Royal Selangor Visitor Centre.</li>
  <li>Transporation: Private Car</li>
  <li>Languages: English (default), Other language services include Mandarin, French, Spanish, Indonesian, Tagalog, Vietnamese, Thai, Japanese, Korean</li>
  <li>Cost: RM 2,000 per person. A surcharge of RM 500 will be imposed for a more customised language tour.</li>
</ul>

